# React Composition

- Split screens by responsibility when a file starts mixing lobby, live race, and result concerns.
- Keep authoritative game state separate from display-only formatting.
- Prefer explicit props and small components over opaque utility layers.
- If the UI needs repeated variants, use composable sections before adding many boolean props.
